 im Verlaufe der Sprachentwicklung und beim Gebrauch der Wörter zum aktuellen Stand der Wortstrukturen führten. Problemorientierte Diskussionen, Musterlösungen, Übungsaufgaben sowie Literaturhinweise zur Vertiefung unterstützen ein selbständiges Bearbeiten des Stoffes.Das erfolgreiche Einführungswerk liegt nun in einer aktualisierten Neuauflage vor.  aThis book covers the full range of aspects concerning the inflection and formation of words in German. It also discusses the structure of the ‘small’ parts of speech and takes into account historical developments. The presentation is separated into introductory and advanced chapters. It is supplemented by numerous examples, discussions, exercises and sample solutions as well as references and an extensive glossary.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman languagexMorphologyxStudy and teaching. 4aFlexion. 4aMorphologie. 4aWortbildung. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / Morphology.2bisacsh  aInflection.  aMorphology.  aWord Formation.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2014z9783110370270oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831103736390 cprintz978311035893340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311036930440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110369304423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110369304/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014  aZDB-23-DSPb2014